      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija Un Mohſus fazzija: Seſa\nus Mohsu: ſapulzina man ſeptin- fimts reiſt tuhkſtoſcht Rahjince\ndeſmits Wihrus no teem Iſraëta irr ſchee Laudis/ ka Widdú\neſmu/ un tu fakki/ es doschu tee\nWezzajeem/ no ka tu finni/ ka tee Galtu/ un teem buhs wec\nto Lauschu Wezzajee/ un winau wiſſaugoſchu Mehneſi ehſt!\nWirſneeki irr/ un dabbu man\n22. Buhs tad masus un le\ntohs preekſch tahs Sa-eefchanas lus Lohpus preekſch teem nokau\nTelts/ un laid tee tur patt ar ka preekſch winneem gann buht\ntewim stahw. Buhs wiſſahn Siwit Juhs\nfapulzinatabin tapſ? ka preekſ\nwinneem gann buhtu?"
